Adding trikz maps to fpsb so it can become its own map type as it should be.

If you made any of the maps i uploaded that wernt here, then speak to me.


Trikz maps:

A trikz map is like an assualt course... Basically all you have to do is get to the end.


To get there thought, you must use glitchs to get height and speed boosts.

You must overcome big heights by nadeboosting, and starjumping, or overcome big lenghts with runboost etc.
